							<h3>IAB</h3>
						</div>
						<div class="col-sm-12 no-padding-div cert-view-content">
							<p style="margin-bottom: 0px">Interactive Advertising Bureau(IAB) Offers IAB Digital Ad Operations Certification. 
							The Certification is available worldwide.
</p>
						</div>
						<div class="col-sm-12 no-padding-div cert-view-content">
							<h4>Digital Ad Operations Certification</h4>
							<div class="col-sm-12">
								<div class="info-div grad1">
									<h5>
										<strong>Criteria</strong>

									</h5>
									<ul>
								<li>A minimum of two (2) years of work experience in Digital Advertising Operations or operational roles in advertising companies</li>
										<li>Eligible candidates will also be required to submit a signed Code of Ethics that all certified individuals must abide by and uphold</li>
										<li>Recertification is required</li>
									</ul>
								</div>

							</div>
							<div class="col-sm-12">
								<div class="info-div grad1">
