										<li>Professionals in digital ad operations at Advertising Agencies, Digital Publishers, 
							Trading Desks, Demand and Supply-Side Platforms, Exchanges and Brands organizations</li>
									</ul>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="col-sm-12">
								<p><a href="http://www.iab.com/iab-ad-ops-certification-overview/">Learn more</a></p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
