							<h3>PPA</h3>
						</div>
						<div class="col-sm-12 no-padding-div cert-view-content">
							<p style="margin-bottom: 0px"> Promotional Products Association (PPA) International is
							the world's largest and oldest international not-for-profit promotional products association. They provide the Trained Advertising Specialist (TAS) certification. 
							TAS Certificate is aimed at providing promotional products professionals with less 
							than 3 years of industry experience an avenue for earning an industry credential</p>
						</div>
						<div class="col-sm-12 no-padding-div cert-view-content">
							<h4>TAS</h4>
							
							<div class="col-sm-12">
								<div class="info-div grad1">
									<h5>
										<strong>Recertification</strong>

									</h5>
									<ul>
										<li>Recertification is compulsoryÂ every three years</li>
										<li>recertification points may be earned through attendance at live industry classes, webinars, PPAI accredited Regional Association education and with approved third-party education</li>
										<li>Membership with PPAI is not a requirement to renew your PPAI Certification</li>
									</ul>
								</div>
		
							</div>
							<div class="col-sm-12">
								<div class="info-div grad1">
									<h5>
										<strong>Levels of TAS certification</strong>

									</h5>
									<ul>
										<li>Certified Advertising Specialist (CAS)</li>
										<li>Master Advertising Specialist (MAS)</li>
										<li>Master Advertising Specialist Plus (MAS+)</li>
										
									</ul>
